menu "MiNOS - System infos"
    config MINOS_SYSINFO_ENABLE
        bool "Enable mn_sysinfo (System infos page)"
        default n
        help
            Adds a /sysinfo page to the HTTPS server and a "System infos" button on the home page.
            The feature is also gated at runtime via g_mn_sysinfo_runtime_enable.
endmenu
